.\}
.el \{\
.sp -1
.IP \(bu 2.3
.\}.PP
\fB\fI{proplist_file, path()}\fR\fR  If this property is defined, \fIInets\fR expects to find all other properties defined in this file. The file must include all properties listed under mandatory properties.

.RE

.PP
\fBNOTE: \fRNote support for legacy configuration file with Apache syntax is dropped in OTP-23.


